{"type": "article", "id": 23672, "title": "打结的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115807PuMrHybXS8l1DiT6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组打结的软垫让人不由自主想躺在上面，以色列的工作室 Knots Studio 使用了木质圆环将它捆扎起来，并做成不同型号和亮丽的颜色，让它变得非常活泼。另有一款安装了木腿作为凳子，型号较小的有 45 厘米宽，更适合儿童，售价 110 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/269396971/medium-dark-blue-white-stripes-cushion?ref=shop_home_active_1\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115805PYNuCRFwaBoO5dnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.52666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115806563whTxylXuGoKWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115806srCSuaDUZOV8iM6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115807prKuzc9SHjnlV2UC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}